track_notes: The road to Auvare is a bit small and long, but this village is fine to visit! there is some fresh water if you need. You can park at the village, or 1km before where is a telecom pylone. The last part of the path to the summit  is not easy to find, in between trees!

This summit is very hard to reach, because of there is no direct path and the slope is very hard in between the forest! Plenty room for antenna and GSM coverage ok, not in summer as it is very hot, best in spring or autumn
